    "49072073": {
      "title": "Lattice versions of quantum field theory models in two dimensions",
      "abstract": "Abstract The quantum inverse scattering method allows one to put quantum field theory models on a lattice in a way which preserves the dynamical structure. The trace identifies are discussed for these models."
